Sentient Shield EDR: Week 1 Progress Report
üõ°Ô∏è Project Overview Sentient Shield is an enterprise-grade Endpoint Detection and Response (EDR) grid designed to protect the Infotact Solutions infrastructure. This project leverages Wazuh to provide real-time visibility, log analysis, and automated response across multiple operating systems.

üë• Team Roles & Responsibilities

Sumit Sharma (Infrastructure Lead): Core SOC deployment, Docker orchestration, and centralized manager configuration.

Chinmai Raj (Linux Analyst): Linux endpoint monitoring, hardening, and Debian-based agent integration.

